| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2794 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ad5e3a46-8b72-50fa-a4d5-9dc5829142ae"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
